    <title>Mehul Nisar &#039;excited&#039; as he completes 18 years as an actor</title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/mehul-nisar-excited-he-completes-18-years-actor-160513</link>
    <description> <p>The ever-smiling <a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/birthday-wishes-harshad-mehul-esha-and-mehul-vyas-150903">Mehul Nisar </a>is a workaholic, and has been going strong in the acting sphere over the last 18 years. The actor who came to the limelight with Hip Hip Hurray years back, has had a satisfying journey as an actor, and believes that he gets paid to do what he loves the most, and that is acting...</p></description>

  <item>
    <title>Karan-Hina have a message for Ashnoor; read for more...</title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/karan-hina-have-message-ashnoor-read-more-160513</link>
    <description> <p>The bubbly and chirpy <a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/rohan-ashnoors-sibling-revelry-160506">Ashnoor Kaur</a>, who’s currently mesmerizing viewers as Naira on Star Plus’ <a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/all-you-need-know-about-the-post-leap-drama-yeh-rishta-160511">Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai</a>, wrapped up her shoot yesterday (12 May).</p><p>As the show is all set to take a leap, Naira would be shown as a grown up. Yesterday, was Ashnoor’s last day on the sets and she has already started missing the show and her co-stars.</p></description>

    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/movie/gossip/have-uday-chopra-nargis-fakhri-called-it-quits-160513</link>
    <description> <p>What’s happening to 2016? Is it truly the most jinxed year for Bollywood? Because we have news coming in that another pair has bit the dust.</p><p>According to a popular entertainment site, Uday has backed off from his marriage to Nargis, which has caused her a major nervous breakdown.</p></description>

  <item>
    <title>Koyal to lose memory in SAB TV&#039;s Chidiya Ghar </title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/koyal-lose-memory-sab-tvs-chidiya-ghar-160513</link>
    <description> <p>After the grand wedding of Gadha Prasad (Jitu Shivhare) and Markati (Aarti Kandpal), SAB TV’s <a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/sangeet-ceremony-sab-tvs-chidiya-ghar-160503">Chidiya Ghar</a> (Garima Prodcutions) is gearing up for an exciting episode.</p><p>The upcoming drama will revolve around Koyal (Aditi Sajwan) who would lose her memory.</p><p>Yes, soon Ghotak (Paresh Ganatra) and Koyal would be seen celebrating their wedding anniversary where Pappi (Sanjay Chaudhary) would plot to take revenge from Ghotak.</p></description>

    <title>Preity Zinta hits back at national daily; accuses it of lying!</title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/movie/movie-news/preity-zinta-hits-back-national-daily-accuses-it-of-lying-160512</link>
    <description> <p>The bubbly B-Town beauty lost her cool on the media for lying blatantly. A tabloid today carried a news story of Preity abusing the coach of Kings XI Punjab, Sanjay Bangar.</p><p>Not someone to take things lying, the actress took to social network and shared her official statement on the issue. She's even threatened to sue the journalists in questions for defamation. Read her whole text here.</p></description>

    <description><br /><strong>Is Sushant nursing a heartbreak? Looks sure like it as he just shared a rather philosophical post on his Instagram profile. The actor, who recently split from girlfriend of many years Ankita Lokhande, took to the photo-sharing app to reveal his sensitive side. </strong><br /><br /><strong>The picture, captioned The REAL Game..!!, was lapped up by his fans and followers. </strong><br /></description>

    <title>Yaaay!! Dhruv Bhandari is back to the bay</title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/yaaay-dhruv-bhandari-back-the-bay-160512</link>
    <description> <p>When you love work, you cannot stay too far from it!</p><p>The dashing <a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/dhruv-bhandaris-dad-mohan-passes-away-150924">Dhruv Bhandari</a> aka Mantu of <em>Tere Sheher Mein</em> has been missing from action. But now the hero is back and how!</p><p>Dhruv, who faced a personal setback with his dad, actor Mohan Bhandari passing away was on a sabbatical from work. And before heading back to the audition rooms, the actor has stepped back on the stage, his first love.</p></description>

    <description> <p>It’s time to witness SAB TV’s <em><a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/balma-and-manisha-elope-saheb-biwi-aur-boss-160509">Saheb Biwi Aur Boss</a>' </em>brand new avatar.</p><p>This Edit II Productions’ comedy show will soon undergo a revamp.</p><p>As per our sources, the series will now have different tales in each episode.     <title>Salman Khan shows &#039;unconditional&#039; love for pet</title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/movie/movie-news/salman-khan-shows-unconditional-love-pet-160512</link>
    <description> <p>Superstar Salman Khan has shared a photograph where he is seen expressing his "unconditional" love towards his pet dog.<br /><br />The 50-year-old shared a photograph of himself kissing his pet. He captioned it: "Unconditional".<br /><br /><em>"Sultan"</em> is said to be based on life of Sultan Ali Khan -- a wrestler who is faced with problems in his professional and personal lives. To get hold of the character in the best possible way, Salman gained weight and underwent rigorous training.<br /></p></description>

  <item>
    <title>To save water, Karan stops shooting</title>
    <link>http://tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/save-water-karan-stops-shooting-160512</link>
    <description> <p>Upset that a lot of water would be wasted amid drought in a shooting sequence, actor <a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/i-am-still-love-karan-kamya-punjabi-160502">Karan Patel</a> refused to shoot for "<a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/wow-ishita-and-mrs-bhalla-meet-yeh-hai-mohabbatein-160511">Yeh Hai Mohabbatein</a>" -- until his concerns were met.<br /><br />Karan had to shoot for a romantic track which required artificial rain, for which a lot of water was to be used. Karan refused to shoot considering the amount of water that would get wasted.<br /></p></description>
     <pubDate>Thursday, May 12, 2016 - 16:30</pubDate>

    <description> <p>Actor<a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/not-mahajan-it-kinshuk-vaidya-sony-tvs-next-160511"> Kinshuk Vaidya</a>, who came into the limelight through his portrayal of Sanju in popular show “Shaka Laka Boom Boom”, is making a comeback on Indian television after a decade with upcoming show “<a href="http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/kavita-barjatya-launches-new-banner-ropes-kinshuk-shivaya-show-160510"><em>Ek Rishta Saajhedari Ka</em></a>”. He says he is “excited” about his return to the small screen.<br /></p></description>
